OL,3,CDad tells murder trial toddler was
OL,4,C'always smiling, always laughing'
OL,6,FA toddler who was allegedly killed by
OL,7,Fhis mother's partner has been
OL,8,Fdescribed as "always smiling, always
OL,9,Flaughing".
OL,11,FCharlie Roberts, who was one year and
OL,12,F10 months old, died at his home in
OL,13,FDarlington in January 2024.
OL,15,FChristopher Stockton, 38, who was in a
OL,16,Frelationship with Charlie's mother
OL,17,FPaula Roberts, is accused of
OL,18,Finflicting a serious brain injury
OL,19,Fwhich could not be survived.
