OL,3,CDad tells murder trial toddler was
OL,4,C'always smiling, always laughing'
OL,6,FHe denies murder and a charge of child
OL,7,Fneglect.
OL,9,FPaula Roberts, 41, is also charged
OL,10,Fwith child neglect, which she denies.
OL,12,FOn Monday (18 November) Charlie's
OL,13,Ffather, Barry Greenwell, gave evidence
OL,14,Fin the trial of Stockton and Roberts
OL,15,Fat Teesside Crown Court.
OL,17,FHe told the jury that his son "was
OL,18,Falways smiling, always laughing,
OL,19,Falways walking around".
