OL,3,CDad tells murder trial toddler was
OL,4,C'always smiling, always laughing'
OL,6,FFour days before Charlie died, Mr
OL,7,FGreenwell told the court that his
OL,8,Fappointment to see his son was
OL,9,Fcancelled because Paula Roberts
OL,10,Fplanned to take the toddler to
OL,11,Fhospital because of a suspected
OL,12,Fconcussion.
OL,14,FHe also described seeing bruises on
OL,15,Fhis son at various points, although he
OL,16,Fsaid there was never anything that
OL,17,Fmade him or his partner feel that they
OL,18,Fhad to raise concerns.
