OL,6,FCharlie's paternal grandfather, Ray
OL,7,FGreenwell also gave evidence, and
OL,8,Fdescribed seeing a bruise "between the
OL,9,Fsize of a squash ball and a tennis
OL,10,Fball" on the toddler's head on Boxing
OL,11,FDay 2023, two-and-a-half weeks before
OL,12,Fhe died.
OL,14,FBoth Stockton and Roberts deny the
OL,15,Fcharges against them.JThe trial
OL,16,Fcontinues.
